      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear like small stone chips, the interior is clean and free of major blemishes. All major systems are functioning as expected, and it has recently undergone a routine inspection.",
