    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic project opportunity! This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back to its best. It's the perfect choice for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper with plenty of potential left to unlock!",
