      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent maintenance history and commendable road presence. This unit has undergone a meticulous professional assessment to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. A premier choice for the sophisticated buyer seeking a balance of luxury and proven reliability.",
