    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well cared for over the years. It's the perfect match for someone looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. I've loved every mile in it, but it's time for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
