      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts a linear power delivery and an 8,400 RPM redline that remains as visceral as ever. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its M Variable Differential Lock to provide exceptional turn-in and corner-exit traction. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a dedicated driver's tool, the powertrain and subframe are in excellent operational order, making this a prime candidate for those who value performance over concours perfection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
